  - "② The draws are independent (with replacement), so $P(\\text{EE}) = P(\\text{even})^2$ and $P(\\text{OO}) = P(\\text{odd})^2$. Target: $P = P(\\text{EE}) + P(\\text{OO})$."
  - "③ $P = \\left(\\frac{2}{5}\\right)^2 + \\left(\\frac{3}{5}\\right)^2 = \\frac{4 + 9}{25} = \\frac{13}{25}$."
tests:
  probability: 1.0
  counting: 0.3
